<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Bem-vindo ao FitCheck</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/logo-fitcheck.png">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .topbar { justify-content: center; }

    .index-container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .icon { width: 96px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 22px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,105,92,0.2); }

    p {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
      color: #4a6360;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00897b, #00695c);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,137,123,0.4);
      transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      min-width: 200px;
    }

    .cta-button:hover { opacity: 0.88; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/img/logo-fitcheck.png" alt="Logo"> FitCheck
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="index-container">
    <h1>Bem-vindo ao <span style="color: #009688;">FitCheck</span> 🩺</h1>

    <img src="/img/logo-fitcheck.png" alt="Logo FitCheck" class="icon">

    <p>Cuide do seu corpo, mente e energia. Registe. Acompanhe. Evolua. 🌱</p>

    <a href="/login" class="cta-button">Começar agora 🚀</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
